Module org.easymock
Package org.easymock

Class Capture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.easymock.Capture<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the captured element
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class Capture<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Will contain what was captured by the capture() matcher. Knows if something was captured or not (allows to capture a null value). Implementation note: If the capture is serialized, it is the user duty to make sure the transformation used also is serializable.
    Author:
    Henri Tremblay
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
